message.body: I think we will go around noon!
Hey! Don't know if I'm gonna make it to the mutter after all! I drank too much last night and am in bed...don't wanna get up for a while still. Hope you
guys have fun! What are you doing after the mutter?

No prob! You need an egg biscuit and a Gatorade! We are meeting up with Alison later this afternoon then maybe getting Chinese for dinner! Probably hang at the house tonight. She's been trying to watch as much American horror story as possible before she leaves
Haha that's amazing. Is she not allowed to watch it at home?
I do need a cheesy egg biscuit.
And Gatorade
They don't have cable or internet at home.
Hahahaha
Oh man. I totally understand then!
Maybe I'll just stop by the house later? KIT!
Do you and hunter want some havarti cheese slices?
A client of mine gave me a big pack of havarti cheese and I don't think we can eat it all.
Lol. This is the funniest text I ever got. Yes we want your cheese
Come stop by tonight!
I will come by later and bring the cheese.
Let me know when you're back at your house and I'll bring you some cheese.
Okay will do!
Come over anytime
We at dinner! How late you guys be up?
Olivia went upstairs to watch TV, she might not make it too late but I'll be up for a bit!
Oh no! I wanted to meet her...I'll let you know when we're heading back!
I think I tired her out! Ha! Let me know. Tmw might be better for a cheese trade if she's in bed!
Ok sounds good! She's gotta watch her hours of American horror story.
She finished season 1. She's watching Prozac Nation now. Is that inappropriate?
